%% Detailed Verint S3 file flow (the corrected path)
%% IntervalAggregator generates files in S3 - Verint folder
%% S3 events trigger VerintPublisher which posts to per-tenant Verint API
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant DDB as DynamoDB<br/>aggregated facts
    participant IA as IntervalAggregator
    participant VRG as VerintReportGenerator
    participant VAG as Verint Agent Profile<br/>Generator
    participant PUB as AwsS3Publisher
    participant S3 as S3 interval bucket<br/>IntegrationsWFMIntervalBucket
    participant Q as SqsVerintPublishQueue
    participant VP as VerintPublisher<br/>Java
    participant AS3 as AwsS3Service
    participant MPS as MessageProcessingService
    participant CSI as CSIQueuePerformanceService
    participant AP as AgentPerformanceService
    participant AUR as Aurora External_GetAllTenantData
    participant V as Verint API<br/>per-tenant

    Note over IA: Triggered by EtlScheduler POST or internal 15 or 30 min cadence
    IA->>DDB: DynamoConnector / DynamoReader
    DDB-->>IA: aggregated facts 15-min window

    Note over IA: IntervalReportGenerator dispatches
    par
        IA->>VRG: generate Verint queue file
        VRG->>PUB: Publish JSON
        PUB->>S3: PutObject verint slash BU TenantId slash yyMMdd.HHmm.json
    and Verint Agent Profile enabled
        IA->>VAG: generate agent file
        VAG->>PUB: Publish JSON
        PUB->>S3: PutObject verintadherence slash BU TenantId slash TTI_yyyyMMdd.HHmm.json
    end

    Note over S3: S3 ObjectCreated event
    S3->>Q: notification bucket and key

    Q->>VP: SqsQueueService listener receives

    VP->>MPS: getFileDetailsFromMessage message
    MPS-->>VP: FileDetails bucket key BU TenantId

    VP->>AS3: fetchFile bucket key
    AS3->>S3: GetObject
    S3-->>AS3: JSON body
    AS3-->>VP: file content

    Note over VP: Filename-based routing
    alt key contains verintadherence and filename starts with TTI underscore
        VP->>AP: format agent-perf payload
        AP->>AUR: CALL External_GetAllTenantData
        AUR-->>AP: tenant config
        AP->>V: POST per-tenant API agent-performance endpoint
    else queue performance file under verint
        VP->>CSI: format queue-perf payload
        CSI->>AUR: CALL External_GetAllTenantData
        AUR-->>CSI: tenant config
        CSI->>V: POST per-tenant API queue-performance endpoint
    end

    V-->>VP: HTTP 2xx
    VP->>Q: DeleteMessage on success
